41:27.880 --> 41:33.440
One of the things that AI is doing right now is that it's questioning the aspect of open source again.

41:33.440 --> 41:38.880
We saw a lot of big companies, as I said, not caring about open source.

41:38.880 --> 41:41.000
Politicians not caring about open source.

41:42.080 --> 41:47.720
